------------ Networking & Resume ------------

❌ Add soft skills to your resume.
❌ Posting on LinkedIn every 1–2 weeks attracts people and visibility.
✅ Improve your GitHub and LinkedIn profiles to attract more attention.
❌ Don’t be shy: talking to recruiters increases your chances of getting a job or internship, whether on LinkedIn or in person.
❌ Do networking: talk to people on LinkedIn or attend events in your state or city. Most people go to these events specifically to network.
❌ Look at job postings on LinkedIn to see the requirements, and use that to discover what the market demands so you can study those topics and add them to your resume.
